---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy - useUtils" 
  description="Learn about our 100% client-side privacy guarantee. We do not transmit, collect, or store any of your private keys or tokens."
  keywords="privacy policy, useutils privacy, local-first privacy, client-side tools security"
>
  <!-- Main Navigation Header -->
  <header class="w-full bg-canvas border-b border-border-hairline h-14 sticky top-0 z-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto h-full px-4 flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2 group">
        <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded bg-accent-emerald flex items-center justify-center font-mono font-black text-black text-sm select-none">
          u
        </div>
        <span class="font-sans font-semibold text-zinc-50 tracking-tight group-hover:text-accent-emerald transition-colors">
          useUtils
        </span>
      </a>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <button
          type="button"
          class="theme-toggle-btn p-2 rounded-lg bg-zinc-900 border border-border-hairline text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-50 hover:bg-zinc-850 transition-all cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-center"
          aria-label="Toggle dark/light theme"
        >
          <svg class="theme-sun-icon w-4.5 h-4.5 hidden" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 3v1m0 16v1m9-9h-1M4 12H3m15.364-6.364l-.707.707M6.343 17.657l-.707.707m12.728 0l-.707-.707M6.343 6.343l-.707-.707M12 8a4 4 0 100 8 4 4 0 000-8z" />
          </svg>
          <svg class="theme-moon-icon w-4.5 h-4.5 hidden" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M20.354 15.354A9 9 0 018.646 3.646 9.003 9.003 0 0012 21a9.003 9.003 0 008.354-5.646z" />
          </svg>
        </button>
        <span class="text-[10px] md:text-xs text-zinc-400 font-mono bg-zinc-900 border border-border-hairline rounded px-2.5 py-1">
          v1.0.0
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Main Body Content -->
  <main class="flex-grow w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 flex flex-col gap-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 pt-2 pb-6 border-b border-border-hairline/60">
      <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-50 font-sans">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans">
        Last updated: June 10, 2026. Your privacy is protected by design: all computations occur entirely inside your browser.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-panel border border-border-hairline rounded-xl p-6 md:p-10 shadow-sm flex flex-col gap-8">
      
      <!-- Section 1 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-50 tracking-tight mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="w-1 h-5 bg-accent-emerald rounded-full"></span>
          1. The Local-First Privacy Guarantee
        </h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans">
          Unlike traditional web utilities that process data on backend servers, <strong class="text-zinc-200">useUtils</strong> functions entirely inside your client browser sandbox. When you encode, decode, sign, or parse tokens and keys, the computations are handled by local JavaScript and Web Crypto APIs.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 2 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-50 tracking-tight mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="w-1 h-5 bg-accent-emerald rounded-full"></span>
          2. No Server Transmission
        </h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans">
          We do not transmit your data over the network. Your keys, claims, secrets, and configuration inputs are never sent to our servers or stored in any database. Your browser console network tab can be audited at any time to verify that zero external network calls are made during utility computations.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 3 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-50 tracking-tight mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="w-1 h-5 bg-accent-emerald rounded-full"></span>
          3. Browser Storage
        </h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans">
          To improve user experience, some tools may store your non-sensitive preferences (such as light or dark theme choices) locally inside your browser's <code class="font-mono text-xs bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 text-zinc-300 rounded px-1.5 py-0.5">localStorage</code>. We never store sensitive credentials, secrets, or keys in local storage.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 4 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-50 tracking-tight mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="w-1 h-5 bg-accent-emerald rounded-full"></span>
          4. Updates to This Policy
        </h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans">
          As our toolset grows, we will continue to adhere to our strict client-side-only execution standard. Any updates to this policy will reflect this core architectural constraint.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer Info Box -->
      <div class="p-4 bg-zinc-900/40 border border-border-hairline rounded-lg flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-accent-emerald shrink-0"></div>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-xs leading-relaxed">
          <strong>Privacy Audit Tool:</strong> You can inspect our source code directly in our repository or view the network tab in your browser's Developer Tools to confirm that no server transmissions occur.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- Footer Section -->
  <footer class="w-full bg-canvas border-t border-border-hairline mt-auto">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 text-xs text-zinc-500">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-2 md:gap-4">
        <span>© 2026 useUtils.com</span>
        <span class="hidden md:inline text-zinc-800">•</span>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <a href="/about" class="hover:text-zinc-350 transition-colors">About Us</a>
          <span class="text-zinc-800">•</span>
          <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-zinc-350 text-accent-emerald transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a>
          <span class="text-zinc-800">•</span>
          <a href="/terms" class="hover:text-zinc-350 transition-colors">Terms & Conditions</a>
          <span class="text-zinc-800">•</span>
          <a href="/contact" class="hover:text-zinc-350 transition-colors">Contact Us</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 font-mono text-[10px]">
        <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-accent-emerald">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent-emerald"></span>
          Processed locally in browser. Zero server transmission.
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
